{"tid":2327722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文匯報狙擊Chickeeduck新鋪指違反國安法，周小龍回應：「唔識文匯報」","createTime":"2020-12-16T09:18:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T09:27:26.000Z","uid":276872,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9476039a1b80cc9997a049ef0c1e1edf13ea14d6","tid":2327722,"uid":276872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:18:39.000Z","msg":"以下轉載100毛Post：<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n\\\\早前因於店舖內擺放民主女神像，而被終止租約嘅童裝店老闆周小龍嘅新店「Chickeeduck藝術生活百貨」今日於天后興發街正式開張，而無論係前幾日試業、定到今日開張，黨報都有報導，相當積極地做另類宣傳。<br />\n <br />\n《文匯》將新店閘門上一張戴豬嘴、眼罩等嘅女生噴畫形容為「女黑魔」（唔知咩term嚟🤷🏻&zwj;♀️），又話店舖嘅裝潢「黑暴意味極濃」、商品又「煽暴宣獨」（？？）咁，質疑周小龍係以取巧嘅方式避開國安法；又指佢哋嘅「記者」亦嘗試訪問周小龍，關於新店嘅裝修同商品「會否涉觸犯香港國安法」咁樣，但就被周小龍一句「唔識文匯報」拒絕作答。<br />\n <br />\n毛毛睇完佢兩篇報導之後，除咗領略到學好中文嘅重要性之外，都想問一問⋯⋯究竟塊文匯布一般會用嚟墊枱底定凳底？<br />\n <br />\n資料來源：文匯報<br />\n圖片來源：周小龍FB//"},{"pid":"e8389c2aa2f113655f93dd50780be71c29d2c9a3","tid":2327722,"uid":276872,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"唔識黨媒，好撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，不過我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c94a2ae50c911649b45f43491638c7ee48430d45","tid":2327722,"uid":276872,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:20:08.000Z","msg":"文匯報依家係收費，究竟有冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9babcca2dc4c8d807841d52075bde5d002db861","tid":2327722,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T09:20:39.000Z","msg":"文?邊度文呀睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bee7c4244dad3fe8ccb3227066e28e1e6d9d8e0","tid":2327722,"uid":2054,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T